quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  2,47,JA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE EDHKURU NI’METIJEL-LETI ‘EN’AMTU ‘ALEJKUM WE ‘ENNI FEDDELTUKUM ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  2,48,WE ETTEKU JEWMÆN LA TEXHZI NEFSUN ‘AN NEFSIN SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JUKBELU MINHA SHEFA’ATUN WE LA JU’UHADHU MINHA ‘ADLUN WE LA HUM JUNSERUNE
  2,49,WE ‘IDH NEXHXHEJNAKUM MIN ‘ALI FIR’AWNE JESUMUNEKUM SU’EL-’ADHABI JUDHEBBIHUNE ‘EBNA’EKUM WE JESTEHJUNE NISA’EKUM WE FI DHALIKUM BELA’UN MIN RABBIKUM ‘ADHIMUN
  2,50,WE ‘IDH FEREKNA BIKUMUL-BEHRE FE’ENXHEJNAKUM WE ‘EGREKNA ‘ALE FIR’AWNE WE ‘ENTUM TENDHURUNE
  2,51,WE ‘IDH WA’ADNA MUSA ‘ERBA’INE LEJLETEN THUMME ETTEHADHTUMUL-’IXHLE MIN BA’DIHI WE ‘ENTUM DHALIMUNE
  2,52,THUMME ‘AFEWNA ‘ANKUM MIN BA’DI DHALIKE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  2,53,WE ‘IDH ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE WEL-FURKANE LE’ALLEKUM TEHTEDUNE
  2,54,WE ‘IDH KALE MUSA LIKAWMIHI JA KAWMI ‘INNEKUM DHELEMTUM ‘ENFUSEKUM BIATTIHADHIKUMUL-’IXHLE FETUBU ‘ILA BARI’IKUM FAKTULU ‘ENFUSEKUM DHALIKUM HAJRUN LEKUM ‘INDE BARI’IKUM FETABE ‘ALEJKUM ‘INNEHU HUWET-TEWWABU ER-REHIMU
  2,55,WE ‘IDH KULTUM JA MUSA LEN NU’UMINE LEKE HETTA NERA ELLAHE XHEHRETEN FE’EHADHETKUMU ES-SA’IKATU WE ‘ENTUM TENDHURUNE
  2,56,THUMME BE’ATHNAKUM MIN BA’DI MEWTIKUM LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  2,57,WE DHELLELNA ‘ALEJKUMUL-GAMAME WE ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJKUMUL-MENNE WE ES-SELWA KULU MIN TEJJIBATI MA REZEKNAKUM WE MA DHELEMUNA WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  2,58,WE ‘IDH KULNA EDHULU HEDHIHIL-KARJETE FEKULU MINHA HEJTHU SHI’TUM REGADÆN WE EDHULUL-BABE SUXHXHEDÆN WE KULU HITTETUN NEGFIR LEKUM HATAJAKUM WE SENEZIDUL-MUHSININE
  2,59,FEBEDDELEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU KAWLÆN GAJREL-LEDHI KILE LEHUM FE’ENZELNA ‘ALEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU RIXHZÆN MINE ES-SEMA’I BIMA KANU JEFSUKUNE